# UI Design — Purrfect Match

Match the Figma mockup at https://sport-linter-78546085.figma.site/

## Tokens

- Background: `#FDF8F3` (cream)
- Text: `#1C1410` (dark brown)
- Muted text: `#6B5E57`
- Accent/success: warm amber for CTAs
- Cards: white, rounded-xl, subtle shadow
- Pills: rounded-full filter chips; active = filled dark

## Layout

- Top nav: logo, Browse, List a Cat, Messages, My Listings, Saved, bell, avatar
- Browse: hero left, filter sidebar, cat grid (3 cols desktop)
- Cat cards: photo, status badge, owner avatar+name, name, breed, fee, rating, location, age, trait pills
- Empty states with helpful copy + CTA button

Mobile: collapse filters into sheet; stack grid to 1 col.
